response.overview: “Biography: Dee Snider” shares the untold story of how Snider went from a high school choir boy to one of the most recognized faces in hard rock. The special depicts the disappointment of record label rejection and how this rejection ultimately led him to write the hit song, “We’re Not Gonna Take It.” Find out just how far success would fuel Snider’s ego before things started to go wrong.
response.title: Biography: Dee Snider
